snippet.title: Game Maker's Toolkit
snippet.description:
Game Maker's Toolkit is a deep dive into game design, level design, and game production, hosted by Mark Brown.

BEFORE YOU EMAIL:

- I do not do sponsored videos, advertising, or integrations on GMTK.
- I am unable to help with individual student school projects
- I do talks, studio visits, and consulting when time allows - let's talk dates and rates!
